TITLE: Custom Hydration Methods for DTOs in LiveComponents
DESCRIPTION: Example of taking full control over DTO hydration by specifying custom methods with hydrateWith and dehydrateWith options on LiveProp.
SOURCE: https://github.com/symfony/ux/blob/2.x/src/LiveComponent/doc/index.rst#2025-04-14_snippet_34

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
class ComponentWithAddressDto
{
    #[LiveProp(hydrateWith: 'hydrateAddress', dehydrateWith: 'dehydrateAddress')]
    public AddressDto $addressDto;

    public function dehydrateAddress(AddressDto $address)
    {
        return [
            'street' => $address->street,
            'city' => $address->city,
            'state' => $address->state,
        ];
    }

    public function hydrateAddress($data): AddressDto
    {
        return new AddressDto($data['street'], $data['city'], $data['state']);
    }
}
```

