TITLE: Custom Stimulus Controller for Component Interaction
DESCRIPTION: JavaScript Stimulus controller that demonstrates how to interact with a LiveComponent, including setting properties and triggering actions.
SOURCE: https://github.com/symfony/ux/blob/2.x/src/LiveComponent/doc/index.rst#2025-04-14_snippet_37

LANGUAGE: javascript
